# Cyber Genie WhatsApp Bot

A WhatsApp chatbot that responds to messages starting with `Cyber Genie, ...` using **OpenAI GPT**.  
Built with **Flask** and **BestCRM API**. No frontend required.

---

## Project Structure

whatsapp_cyber_genie/
├─ app.py # Flask app
├─ requirements.txt # Python dependencies
├─ .env # API keys & tokens
└─ README.md # This file


---

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt

Set environment variables in .env:
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key
BESTCRM_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_bestcrm_access_token
PHONE_NUMBER_ID=your_whatsapp_phone_number_id

Run the app:
python app.py

Configure your BestCRM webhook to point to:
http://<your-server>/webhook